First Department,

February, 1957

(February 2, 1957) In the Matter of Jean A. Vincent et al., Appellants, against Vanderton Realty Corp. et al., Respondents.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondents. No opinion. Concur — Breitel, J. P., Rabin, Frank and Valente, JJ.
